1. *Riješiti* ću to pitanje za sutra. (I will solve this issue for tomorrow.)
2. Ona je *riješila* problem brzo. (She solved the problem quickly.)
3. *Riješavali* smo problem u paru. (We were solving the problem together.)
4. Nismo *riješili* problem na vrijeme. (We didn't solve the problem on time.)
5. Mi ćemo *riješiti* sve probleme. (We'll solve all the problems.)